      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "1. Overview"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "The stored procedure "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "usp_Published_AccountAndMeterListing_ExcelExport",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " is designed to generate a report of account and meter listings for a specified agency and facility. It retrieves data from a view and logs the report usage. The procedure is intended for exporting data to Excel, as suggested by its name. It handles different scenarios based on whether the user is an agency user and whether a specific facility number is provided."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
